"— Dreams of sexual intercourse with a beautiful elven princess: one hour;\n"
"— Dreams of vigorous sexual intercourse with a squad of muscular southern "
"mercenaries: half an hour;\n"
"— Dreams of sexual intercourse with Her Majesty the Queen before, on, and "
